  ('dietitian-moex-00406', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-113-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '李小姐體重65公斤，每日熱量攝取約2,500大卡，若想要在60天內減輕至60公斤，除了每日運動消耗300大卡 熱量外，每日熱量攝取約需控制在多少大卡才能達成減重目標？', '["1,200", "1,500", "1,800", "2,100"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:50+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a4584eaadc9d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8cbef348e467", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113030", "c": "102", "s": "44", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "營養學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 21, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-00407', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-113-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關飢餓素（ghrelin）的敘述，下列何者正確？', '["飢餓素由下視丘分泌，在兩餐之間濃度升高", "飢餓素間接刺激神經胜肽Y（neuropeptide Y）分泌，增強飢餓感", "飢餓素與腦下垂體受器結合，增強飢餓感", "飽食後胰島素濃度上升，抑制飢餓素的分泌"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:50+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a4584eaadc9d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8cbef348e467", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113030", "c": "102", "s": "44", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "營養學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 22, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-00408', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-113-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '穀胱甘肽（glutathione）代謝過程中需要維生素B 以何種型式擔任何種酵素的輔酶？ 2', '["核黃素腺嘌呤雙核苷酸（FAD），穀胱甘肽過氧化酶（glutathione peroxidase）", "核黃素腺嘌呤雙核苷酸（FAD），穀胱甘肽還原酶（glutathione reductase）", "核黃素單核苷酸（FMN），穀胱甘肽過氧化酶（glutathione peroxidase）", "核黃素單核苷酸（FMN），穀胱甘肽還原酶（glutathione reductase）"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:50+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a4584eaadc9d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8cbef348e467", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113030", "c": "102", "s": "44", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "營養學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 23, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
